    // Fluid Core
    hex (0 1 2 3 4 5 6 7) fluid (10 10 100) simpleGrading (1 1 1)

    // Fluid Outer Ring
    hex (8 9 1 0 12 13 5 4) fluid (10 10 100) simpleGrading (1 1 1)
    hex (1 9 10 2 5 13 14 6) fluid (10 10 100) simpleGrading (1 1 1)
    hex (3 2 10 11 7 6 14 15) fluid (10 10 100) simpleGrading (1 1 1)
    hex (11 8 0 3 15 12 4 7) fluid (10 10 100) simpleGrading (1 1 1)

    // Solid Wall Ring
