    hex (9 17 18 10 13 21 22 14) solid (4 10 100) simpleGrading (1 1 1) // Right (Rad=4, Tan=10)
    hex (11 10 18 19 15 14 22 23) solid (10 4 100) simpleGrading (1 1 1) // Top (Tan=10, Rad=4)
    hex (19 16 8 11 23 20 12 15) solid (10 4 100) simpleGrading (1 1 1) // Left (Tan=10, Rad=4)
);

